{"tid":95394,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"喂屌，呢度唔係好多人關心柏洋嘅咩？","createTime":"2017-01-26T04:03:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-27T02:03:00.000Z","uid":65062,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"df5880319bf17c1d2df5b9c43af1e377ab4d32e3","tid":95394,"uid":65062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T04:03:24.000Z","msg":"【魚蛋革命案被重判監禁九個月  柏洋獲保釋候審可與家人團年】<br />\n<br />\n熱血公民成員柏洋被指涉及去年初一旺角事件中，涉嫌襲警及拒捕罪，被判九個月監禁的案件，今日（1月26日）再向法庭進行申請保釋等候上訴，最終申請成功，並將於今日獲釋，可與家人一同團年。<br />\n<br />\n熱血公民成員柏洋被指涉及參與去年大年初一晚至初二凌晨發生的「魚蛋革命」，被控襲警及拒捕案。案件於去年10月6日在九龍城裁判法院宣判，裁判官蘇惠德判處柏洋襲警、拒捕兩項控罪罪成，襲警罪被判九個月監禁，拒捕則判四個月，即時監禁，同期執行，拒絕保釋。雖然柏洋曾經於11月中旬申請保釋等候上訴，但遭法庭以上訴得直機會低為由駁回。<br />\n<br />\n全文︰<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/01-26-2017/35509\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F01-26-2017%2F35509&d=d2yxd3y3fXcjSCKVnkSSFgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=f464afbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/01-26-2017/35509</a><br />\n<br />\n你地成日講撚到柏洋比黃洋達賣撚咗，講到自己好似好關心人咁，依家柏洋成功保釋，過年前終於可以番屋企團年，你地盲咗睇唔到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n祝賀柏洋，希望一切安好。"},{"pid":"8d3472a9edb629834c7e676fa8ac645406edc0cb","tid":95394,"uid":16970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T04:19:09.000Z","msg":"唔好再請當值律師喇."},{"pid":"3254d463ba2c4b9a8518380f6c87e37cdc5a185c","tid":95394,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T04:32:46.000Z","msg":"in 刁t lawyer we trust<br />\nin鳩達 we trust<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zselut7d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzselut7d&h=ed03f39c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sXgpI5jYCOc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsXgpI5jYCOc&d=d2yxd3y3fXcjSCKVnkSSFgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=b7eb057b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sXgpI5jYCOc</a>"},{"pid":"8a4caa97ecad8ae66f6